{"tid":2239766,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"方國珊200萬選舉費無單據 林卓廷報廉署","createTime":"2020-10-12T08:09:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T08:57:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ccd5684b9dafe3545eb411c5bca1bfa0f267bbb5","tid":2239766,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T08:09:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201012/26F23VH4J5DOTGCLXDB4GGORBA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201012%2F26F23VH4J5DOTGCLXDB4GGORBA%2F&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBQuBxQMtbc6xR8MkqxZcasw%3D&h=cbc80b83\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201012%2F26F23VH4J5DOTGCLXDB4GGORBA%2F&h=769824a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201012/26F23VH4J5DOTGCLXDB4GGORBA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n方國珊200萬選舉費無單據 林卓廷報廉署<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HNWPlVoyckEjzbBOkPEf_B6H4jY=/1302x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JVZKHWRU7ZCGZEX7KR7QIQD7QU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHNWPlVoyckEjzbBOkPEf_B6H4jY%3D%2F1302x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJVZKHWRU7ZCGZEX7KR7QIQD7QU.jpg&h=b1da7380&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■林卓廷（左）要求方國珊公開交代全部選舉經費及公開所有單據。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】立法會選舉押後一年，今年候選人申報的選舉開支會獲政府全額退還，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷昨召開記者會，質疑方國珊於政府叫停選舉前兩日即7月29日報名參選，卻申報260萬元選舉開支，而方上屆參選整場選舉僅申報131萬元，2018年補選亦只花不足100萬，差距之大惹人質疑。<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷團隊翻查方國珊的申報，發現近80%開支欠缺單據，包括疑來自關係密切者的捐贈，指方申報225萬元服務及現金捐贈中，105萬元來自由方國珊有份任董事的公司「專業動力」，專業動力註冊地址業主「Hui Yuk Kau」亦為捐款人，相信為方契媽許玉球，捐出現金30萬元，以及每人一萬元、共價值30萬元的30名選舉助理。另一捐贈者「Lau Bik Noon」也捐贈15名同樣每人價值一萬元選舉助理，登記地址業主為「Fong Chong」，與方父親英文名相符。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n參選兩日 助理開支90萬<br />\n<br />\n林更質疑，有關申報並無單據提供，如專業動力捐出12萬元網上宣傳費用，未於選舉廣告申報項目中顯示，「自己聲稱自己友巨額捐贈服務畀自己選，但冇提供單據，然後問政府攞巨額資助，淨袋227萬（元），咁講唔講得通呢？」<br />\n<br />\n林亦質疑方國珊聲稱員工開支實為「幽靈員工」，指方參選兩日，代理人及選舉助理開支為90萬元，但當中65萬元沒有任何簽收單據或員工工時紀錄，令人質疑沒有因應政府突叫停選舉，按比例分攤開支。<br />\n<br />\n以往選舉參選人先要取得5%或以上有效選票再向政府申領資助，而資助上限計算方法是每票15元，或法定選舉開支上限一半，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9NRY0FAgLtUpTAtzAdSSqHAL_n4=/712x728/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DW7B52UHQRELRMNHA54JQJM2M4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9NRY0FAgLtUpTAtzAdSSqHAL_n4%3D%2F712x728%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDW7B52UHQRELRMNHA54JQJM2M4.jpg&h=bdba5338&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n方國珊"},{"pid":"696509b1faaad7fd8ee2ebf6b74ce18b1020b952","tid":2239766,"uid":58841,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T08:10:28.000Z","msg":"今舖fat fat了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62146e7140f84d6d057cc7abac2c758b0b8959d9","tid":2239766,"uid":78968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"696509b1faaad7fd8ee2ebf6b74ce18b1020b952","tid":2239766,"uid":58841,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T08:10:28.000Z","msg":"今舖fat fat了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T08:11:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95d7b9b8f4e9c22176d7fa7590a154bac2003ad5","tid":2239766,"uid":364798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62146e7140f84d6d057cc7abac2c758b0b8959d9","tid":2239766,"uid":78968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"696509b1faaad7fd8ee2ebf6b74ce18b1020b952","tid":2239766,"uid":58841,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T08:10:28.000Z","msg":"今